import { NavLink } from "react-router-dom";
import styles from "./Navbar.module.css";
function Navbar() {
  return (
    <>
      <nav className={styles.navbar}>
        <NavLink to="/" className={`${styles.logo} ${styles.inActiveStyle}`}>
          Shammaas
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink
          to="/"
          className={({ isActive }) =>
            isActive ? styles.activeStyle : styles.inActiveStyle
          }
        >
          Home
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink
          to="/crypto"
          className={({ isActive }) =>
            isActive ? styles.activeStyle : styles.inActiveStyle
          }
        >
          CryptoCurriencies
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink
          to="/blogs"
          className={({ isActive }) =>
            isActive ? styles.activeStyle : styles.inActiveStyle
          }
        >
          Blogs
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink
          to="/submit"
          className={({ isActive }) =>
            isActive ? styles.activeStyle : styles.inActiveStyle
          }
        >
          Submit a Blog
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink
          to="/log-in"
          className={({ isActive }) =>
            isActive ? styles.activeStyle : styles.inActiveStyle
          }
        >
          Log In
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink
          to="/sign-up"
          className={({ isActive }) =>
            isActive ? styles.activeStyle : styles.inActiveStyle
          }
        >
          <button>Sign</button>
        </NavLink>
      </nav>
    </>
  );
}
export default Navbar;
